    "course_title": "TECHNICAL THEATRE FUNDAMENTALS",
    "description": "Learn how to mount a theatrical production. Through scenery, costumes, lighting, sound, and stage management explore the relationship between the technical components of the production process. Includes lectures as well as practical experience in University Theatre productions.",
